        <section id="id18180838">
          <title>BRAIN TEASER!</title>
          <para id="id18204238">Vusi is a passenger on a ferry. He notes that at the first stop 18 people get on and 13 get off. At the next stop 41 people get on and 29 get off. At the third stop 53 people get on and 27 get off. If there were then 233 people left on the ferry, how many people were on the ferry when Vusi got on?</para>
