    <section id="id18275196">
      <title>Assessment</title>
      <para id="id18241173"><emphasis><emphasis effect="italics">Learning Outcome 1:</emphasis></emphasis>The learner will be able to recognise, describe and represent numbers and their relationships, and to count, estimate, calculate and check with competence and confidence in solving problems.</para>
      <para id="id18240909"><emphasis><emphasis effect="italics">Assessment Standard 1.10:</emphasis></emphasis> We know this when the learner uses a range of techniques to perform written and mental calculations with whole numbers including:</para>
      <para id="id18203948"><emphasis effect="bold">1.10.5:</emphasis> using a calculator.</para>
